parameters.name: rates
parameters.description: Data for selected rate channel  by energy step

parameters.name: rates_time
parameters.description: ---> Rate data for the rate channels sorted by energy step with dimension (NUM_DISTS, NRATE, NENERGY) units=counts/s (time_series)

parameters.name: valid
parameters.description: ---> Validity flag codes valid data (bit 0), test pulser on (bit 1), diag mode (bit 2), data comp type (bit 3-4), packet compn (bit 5)

parameters.name: swp_ind
parameters.description: ---> Index that identifies the energy and deflector sweep look up tables (LUT) for the sensor
